oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry Kitty Wells Show at the Lenawee County Fairgrounds
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Wells, Kitty; Wright, Johnnie, 1914-2011; Phillips, Bill (Vocalist); Wright, Bobby; Newman, Jimmy C.;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Kitty Wells, Jimmy C. Newman, Ken Allen, Johnny Wright, Bill Phillips and Bobby Wright at the Lenawee County Fairgrounds on July 18. Poster features metal photoplates of Kitty Wells, Jimmy C. Newman, Ken Allen, Johnny Wright, Bill Phillips, Bobby Wright.
